1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,937
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,239
Don't run!

4
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,600
You two, slow down.

5
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,320
Over there!

6
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,239
- Slow down!
- To the left.

7
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:22,920
A bit higher.

8
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:23,719
Right, right there.

9
00:00:23,719 --> 00:00:24,600
Can't you two

10
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,679
see the massive holes?

11
00:00:26,239 --> 00:00:26,879
Uncle,

12
00:00:26,879 --> 00:00:28,525
why aren't you on the roof

13
00:00:28,525 --> 00:00:29,766
with Brother Buyu?

14
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:32,840
You call Mao Buyu "Brother",

15
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,560
but you call me "Uncle"?

16
00:00:35,679 --> 00:00:38,079
The money for your house and school

17
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,399
all came from me!

18
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,159
Brother Constable, then.

19
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:42,719
That's more like it.

20
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:43,960
Good boy.

21
00:00:45,079 --> 00:00:47,000
Brother Constable,
are you also afraid of heights

22
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:47,719
like me?

23
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:50,159
Me? Afraid of heights?

24
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:50,920
I...

25
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,479
The wealthy provide the funds,

26
00:00:52,479 --> 00:00:53,600
the poor provide the labor.

27
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:55,000
A handsome, dashing,

28
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,679
and elegant young man like me

29
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,759
obviously shouldn't be doing roof work.

30
00:00:58,759 --> 00:00:59,920
I should just sit here

31
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,880
and supervise them.

32
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,119
One more time!

33
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,719
(Ms. Lotus.)

34
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,319
Again, again!

35
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:21,920
I have to win this time.

36
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,079
Hello, Ms. Lotus. I am...

37
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,159
One more time.

38
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,159
Gao Shun, you...

39
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:29,920
Chang!

40
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:30,840
You're here.

41
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,200
Why did you climb so high?

42
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,879
Aren't you tired?

43
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:35,200
I'm looking over the house for them.

44
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,480
It's almost finished anyway.

45
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,959
(Buyu and Yunchang?)

46
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,319
(My dear Ms. Lotus)

47
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:43,359
(is actually Chu Yunchang!)

48
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:46,920
The doctor just checked Grandma's pulse.

49
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,560
He said she's just hungry.

50
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,290
She'll be fine
as long as she eats on time.

51
00:01:50,690 --> 00:01:52,519
I got her some medicine
to boost her vitality.

52
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,239
Again, again!

53
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:56,680
Grandma, here is your medicine.

54
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:58,120
Thank you, Miss.

55
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,239
Go on. Go thank the young man.

56
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:02,879
Quickly.

57
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:06,280
- Thank you, Brother Buyu!
- Thank you!

58
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,200
Get up, get up.

59
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,240
I'm the one who paid!

60
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,560
Everyone, get up. Quick.

61
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,479
Take it from me.

62
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,879
No matter how hard life gets,

63
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,960
never become thieves.

64
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,479
Yes.

65
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:17,039
If you run into trouble in the future,

66
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:18,199
find me at the Gate Bureau.

67
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:21,360
Or you can find Gao Shun.

68
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,039
And me!

69
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,120
I can help too.

70
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,639
Live an honest life.

71
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:27,240
When you grow up, you should all
become constables, alright?

72
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,719
(Sipai Parlor)
Miss, take a look.

73
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,159
Chang, all of these must have been

74
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,960
your uncle's arrangements.

75
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,000
No, thank you.

76
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,919
How did you know?

77
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,599
I don't just know that.

78
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:42,240
I also know his intention.

79
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,639
Buyu, you...

80
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:47,960
There are indeed some heroic thieves

81
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,560
or outlaws in the Sacred Hand Sect.

82
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:51,240
But Chang,

83
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,879
it's possible that your aunt and uncle

84
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,879
are also members of that sect.

85
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:57,919
But they...

86
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,560
It's fine.

87
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,080
Let me finish.

88
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,639
Chang,

89
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,919
I'll say it again.

90
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,400
A thief is a thief,

91
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,719
and I am an officer.

92
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,319
My duty is to catch thieves.

93
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:11,639
Please pass this message to your uncle.

94
00:03:12,887 --> 00:03:14,687
If anyone in the sect
wants to surrender,

95
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,199
I will deal with them by the law.

96
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,560
No extrajudicial punishment.

97
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:21,039
I will never wrong an innocent person.

98
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,159
Let's go.

99
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,800
He reported himself

100
00:03:31,830 --> 00:03:33,719
and even paid them back
out of his own pocket?

101
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,719
He even said Dabao

102
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:38,240
should join the Gate Bureau

103
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,199
to catch thieves with him.

104
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,240
Seriously,

105
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:43,240
why is he so unshakeable?

106
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,560
Mao Buyu really is upright

107
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,800
and open-hearted.

108
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,159
Uncle,

109
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,159
why don't you try again?

110
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,680
Let him just keep
being a famous constable.

111
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,680
Forget it.

112
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,680
From now on, this is no longer my concern.

113
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,960
But don't say I didn't warn you.

114
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,479
If you get hurt later,

115
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,759
don't come crying to us.

116
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,319
Don't worry.

117
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,879
Even if I hit a wall,

118
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,120
I'll find my own corner to cry.

119
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,680
Everyone!

120
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,199
Starting today,

121
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,960
Wushuang is officially reinstated.

122
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,960
She is still Deputy.

123
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,360
- That's great news!
- Excellent!

124
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,319
Cousin Wushuang,

125
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,639
I've been waiting for you!

126
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:19,160
We're not family in the Gate Bureau.
Stay away from me.

127
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:19,800
This is good news.

128
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,040
Yes, we can work cases
with Deputy Luo again.

129
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,279
I'll be counting on all of you for help.

130
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:25,100
Let's solve cases
and catch thieves together.

131
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,639
You're too kind, Deputy Luo.

132
00:04:26,639 --> 00:04:27,160
Buyu.

133
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,290
You'll be partners
with Wushuang from now on.

134
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:32,800
Yu.

135
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,800
We can work cases together again.

136
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,800
I'm counting on you, Wushuang.

137
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,000
The candle is almost out.

138
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,839
Go get some more.

139
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,079
Zhizhi.

140
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,800
Old scoundrel, what do you want?

141
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,279
I, Dongfang Qing,
Leader of the Southern Thieves,

142
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:15,240
pay respects to the Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect.

143
00:05:17,825 --> 00:05:19,362
(Benevolent Martial World)

144
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,600
Dongfang Qing.

145
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,120
You crawled out of a pile of corpses

146
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,839
to come to the Capital.

147
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:30,439
Are you here to challenge us
or for revenge?

148
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,879
It doesn't seem
to be your place to speak.

149
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,879
Sect Leader Dongfang.

150
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,879
Then, what do you want?

151
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,519
I want to negotiate.

152
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,439
Negotiate?

153
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:50,680
Indeed.

154
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,800
I was supposed to be a dead man.

155
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,800
I have no wish to meddle in old feuds.

156
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:58,399
But my two disciples ignored my warnings

157
00:05:58,759 --> 00:06:00,920
and sought out your sect on their own.

158
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:03,680
They brought that purely on themselves.

159
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,959
I have no intention
of seeking revenge for them.

160
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:10,480
Then, you rise from the dead

161
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,399
and travel all this way to the Capital

162
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,879
just to tell me that?

163
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,079
If it were
for those two unfilial disciples,

164
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:19,680
I certainly wouldn't
have come all this way.

165
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:22,560
However, Jade Squirrel,

166
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:25,920
you stole my treasure
right in front of me.

167
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,120
That seems

168
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,839
like a bit of a blatant provocation.

169
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,519
When did I ever steal your treasure?

170
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,040
That is no longer important.

171
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,319
Regardless, it belonged
to the Chu family in the first place.

172
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:41,839
By treasure, surely you don't mean
the Sacred Token?

173
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,240
I won't fall for it.

174
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:49,600
You won't get a word out of me.

175
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:53,279
Right now, I feel threatened.

176
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,399
I want a resolution.

177
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,279
Then, what do you want?

178
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,000
A wager between us.

179
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,240
Why should I trust you?

180
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:02,839
It couldn't be like

181
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:05,079
the way Lin Xin'er deceived
my aunt last time?

182
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,399
This wouldn't be

183
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:10,040
a traditional trick
of the Southern Thieves, would it?

184
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,240
You don't have to trust me.

185
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:13,800
In that case, the Sacred Hand Sect

186
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:16,519
and my Southern Thieves will be
at war from now on.

187
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:19,000
The Martial World will be
bathed in blood once more,

188
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,360
and there will never be peace.

189
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,360
Is this what you want to see?

190
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,839
And if I win,

191
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:27,959
what then?

192
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,399
If you win,

193
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,240
not only can you reclaim
the Sacred Token,

194
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,279
but I will also tell you
a secret from years ago.

195
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:38,839
I will reveal who pulled the strings
behind us four brothers,

196
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:41,100
the mastermind who ordered us
to steal the Sacred Token.

197
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,920
So there was a mastermind after all.

198
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,920
And if I lose?

199
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,759
If you fail to defeat me,

200
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,720
then all the power of your sect

201
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:53,079
will be handed over
to the Southern Thieves.

202
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,920
And you, the Jade Squirrel,

203
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,519
will retire from the Martial World

204
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,560
for good.

205
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,680
You have quite an appetite.

206
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:07,079
Fine. I accept.

207
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,279
Spoken like a true leader.

208
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:13,040
The youth are indeed formidable.

209
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,680
Enough talk.

210
00:08:15,730 --> 00:08:16,519
What is the wager?

211
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:19,879
A contest of thievery, naturally.

212
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,480
There is an item that isn't worth much,

213
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:23,959
but is incredibly hard to obtain.

214
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:27,439
Three days from now,
at the stroke of midnight.

215
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:30,240
Whoever retrieves it first wins.

216
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:31,959
What is it?

217
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:37,240
Commissioner Luo's identification token
from the Gate Bureau.

218
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,287
- A token?
- What?

219
00:08:38,287 --> 00:08:39,240
What?

220
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,120
Stealing from the Gate Bureau?

221
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:52,759
And stealing
the Commissioner's token at that?

222
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:54,399
What is this?

223
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,799
It's a suicide mission.

224
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:59,519
You might as well say you're stealing
the Imperial Seal.

225
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:01,679
At least then the boast
would be more impressive.

226
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,759
That old man is up to no good.

227
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:06,279
Call off this wager.

228
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,120
If I back out now,

229
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:12,159
wouldn't that be the same
as admitting defeat?

230
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,559
But this is no laughing matter.

231
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,080
I'm not actually afraid
of that Commissioner.

232
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,240
I'm just afraid

233
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,039
that Mao Buyu might be patrolling there.

234
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,240
The one you should be worried about

235
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,039
is your rival, Luo Wushuang.

236
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:34,120
All Chang fears is Mao Buyu.

237
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,759
Then, we just need
an opportunity to lure him away.

238
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:40,279
Just like that,
and the Gate Bureau is safe.

239
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,799
Uncle is right.

240
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,440
As long as Mao Buyu isn't there,

241
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,519
I have nothing to fear.

242
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,799
Wait a minute.

243
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:49,399
He's a complete workaholic.

244
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:52,480
How can we keep him out of the picture?

245
00:09:56,679 --> 00:10:00,840
Xu Anran.

246
00:10:07,162 --> 00:10:09,225
(Mao's Residence)

247
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,440
A vacation?

248
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:12,480
Yes.

249
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,399
Why go on a vacation

250
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:15,679
out of the blue?

251
00:10:16,700 --> 00:10:18,039
It's not exactly out of the blue.

252
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,120
I was thinking that the whole family

253
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,879
hasn't been out together in a long time.

254
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,080
Especially you.

255
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,519
You've been so busy with work.

256
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,759
It must be exhausting.

257
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,080
So I thought I'd take this chance

258
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,759
to invite Father and Buyu.

259
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,279
Oh, and Chang too.

260
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,559
Our whole family

261
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:34,360
can go to Tangshan for a couple of days

262
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,679
to relax and unwind.

263
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,679
The whole family?

264
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,600
Including Yunchang?

265
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,879
It's been so hectic lately.

266
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,600
Everyone's been so busy.

267
00:10:45,610 --> 00:10:46,435
The fatigue is real.

268
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:51,919
Why don't we go
to the Tangshan hot springs?

269
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,360
The hot springs?

270
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,919
Just the two of us?

271
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,080
What are you thinking?

272
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,879
The whole family is coming, of course.

273
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,240
Chang.

274
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:04,799
Are your aunt and uncle coming?

275
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,519
No, they aren't.

276
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:07,759
They go out all the time.

277
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:08,919
They won't mind missing this one.

278
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,639
This is mostly for you.

279
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:13,039
You work hard every day
handling all those cases.

280
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:15,240
You've been under
a lot of stress lately.

281
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,200
I just thought

282
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:18,279
we could take this chance

283
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,360
to go and relax for a bit.

284
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,399
That's all there is to it?

285
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,679
What else would it be?

286
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,840
That's great.

287
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,279
It's a perfect chance
to spend quality time with my family.

288
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:33,679
I want to become
a part of your family soon.

289
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,080
Exactly. You know me best.

290
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,000
Let's go home and tell my father.

291
00:11:43,062 --> 00:11:44,639
(Tangshan Hot Spring Inn)

292
00:11:44,639 --> 00:11:45,960
This inn is built on a mountain,

293
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,060
right next to a hot spring.

294
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:49,279
It's a wonderful place for a getaway.

295
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,679
It really is a lovely place.

296
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:55,720
Does it mean we can enjoy the hot spring

297
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,919
without even leaving the inn?

298
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:58,240
This lady is correct.

299
00:11:58,380 --> 00:12:00,159
We can even pipe the water
into your rooms.

300
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:02,600
However, I'd highly recommend
the outdoor pools.

301
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:03,360
Very well.

302
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,240
My dear,

303
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,120
let's get settled and go for a soak.

304
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,679
All right.

305
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,000
Innkeeper,

306
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,480
lead us to our rooms first.

307
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,200
Certainly.

308
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,240
The four premium rooms
have long been prepared.

309
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,039
Please, follow me.

310
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,600
Yes.

311
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,200
Buyu.

312
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:19,320
Chang.

313
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,639
Why didn't your father come?

314
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:25,580
He received an urgent notice
just before we left.

315
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,390
He can't take any leave
for the next few days.

316
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:30,320
That truly is a shame.

317
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,039
Let's go.

318
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:37,240
(Commissioner Luo's identification
token from the Gate Bureau?)

319
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:40,960
(Three days from now,
at the stroke of midnight.)

320
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,879
(Whoever retrieves it first wins.)

321
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:46,399
Chang.

322
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:48,879
Aren't you coming for a soak?

323
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:51,399
Buyu,

324
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,320
I'm not feeling very well.

325
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:55,240
I think I'll turn in early.

326
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:56,960
All right.

327
00:12:59,525 --> 00:13:00,687
(Premium Room Six)

328
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,440
Buyu,

329
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:04,039
aren't you and Chang coming for a soak?

330
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:06,440
Chang said she isn't feeling well.

331
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,100
She doesn't feel like going.

332
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,720
Then, I won't go either.

333
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:10,600
I see.

334
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,639
(Premium Room Six)
Not feeling well?

335
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,600
It's likely that time of the month.

336
00:13:16,799 --> 00:13:18,200
Dear, let's head out.

337
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:18,679
All right.

338
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,679
After you, Madam.

339
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:32,519
Buyu,

340
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:34,679
have you heard about
the wager in the casinos?

341
00:13:34,679 --> 00:13:37,200
It's between the Martial Alliance
and the Southern Thieves.

342
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:39,919
They say that the scoundrel Dongfang Qing,
who faked his death for years,

343
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:42,480
has challenged the Jade Squirrel
to avenge his disciples.

344
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,120
I also heard that

345
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,320
the challenge will take place
here at the Gate Bureau.

346
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:49,080
What?

347
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,200
Such arrogance!

348
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:04,612
(Bureau of Justice)

349
00:14:06,512 --> 00:14:07,862
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

350
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,559
Who's there?

351
00:14:13,279 --> 00:14:14,600
The mighty Gate Bureau's security

352
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:17,440
is quite underwhelming.

353
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,720
You're asking for it!

354
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,559
Are you looking for me?

355
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:27,679
Catch me if you can!

356
00:14:33,912 --> 00:14:35,162
(Bureau of Justice)

357
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:39,720
Split up! After him!

358
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:48,039
(This is going almost too smoothly.)

359
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:50,679
(Now, where could that
old scoundrel be?)

360
00:15:09,562 --> 00:15:12,837
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

361
00:15:12,875 --> 00:15:15,750
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

362
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:21,968
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

363
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:26,470
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

364
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:29,520
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

365
00:15:30,688 --> 00:15:35,928
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

366
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:39,543
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

367
00:15:39,543 --> 00:15:43,193
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

368
00:15:43,262 --> 00:15:46,752
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

369
00:15:46,850 --> 00:15:49,825
♪To the ends of time♪

370
00:15:49,825 --> 00:15:53,200
♪The moon traces your face♪

371
00:15:53,387 --> 00:15:56,975
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

372
00:15:56,975 --> 00:16:03,215
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

373
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:06,765
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

374
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:10,588
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

375
00:16:10,875 --> 00:16:13,900
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

376
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:17,000
♪On our way to forever♪

377
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:20,850
♪The moon traces your face♪

378
00:16:20,850 --> 00:16:24,210
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

379
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:30,360
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

380
00:16:31,437 --> 00:16:41,077
♪Just to be with you♪
